00:40:08,400 --> 00:40:09,360
I can tell

858
00:40:09,840 --> 00:40:11,220
that you have a good eye for nice stuff.

859
00:40:11,220 --> 00:40:12,550
To know if the pill is true,

860
00:40:12,550 --> 00:40:13,630
just sniff it.

861
00:40:15,920 --> 00:40:17,700
I wouldn't sell it to someone else

862
00:40:17,700 --> 00:40:19,900
if I weren't in desperate need of money.

863
00:40:20,150 --> 00:40:20,880
I believe

864
00:40:21,360 --> 00:40:22,800
you're a sophisticated man

865
00:40:22,800 --> 00:40:24,190
with many talents.

866
00:40:24,710 --> 00:40:26,760
I'm sure you know how good this pill is.

867
00:40:26,760 --> 00:40:28,400
It's fate that brought us here today.

868
00:40:28,400 --> 00:40:30,460
I'll only charge you 8 taels of silver

869
00:40:30,880 --> 00:40:31,620
for this

870
00:40:31,800 --> 00:40:32,800
Sword Heart Pill.

871
00:40:33,030 --> 00:40:34,690
I think it'll be in good hands.

872
00:40:37,880 --> 00:40:39,210
It is indeed a good pill.

873
00:40:39,800 --> 00:40:41,130
But my master forbids me

874
00:40:41,240 --> 00:40:42,070
from taking other pills

875
00:40:42,070 --> 00:40:43,600
than those made in the sect.

876
00:40:44,110 --> 00:40:45,800
What a shame!

877
00:40:49,320 --> 00:40:50,050
Give it to me.

878
00:40:50,280 --> 00:40:50,940
I'll buy it.

879
00:40:52,440 --> 00:40:53,300
It's yours now.

880
00:40:57,480 --> 00:40:59,440
If I eat this pill at the foot of the mountain,

881
00:40:59,440 --> 00:41:01,170
Master might not figure it out.

882
00:41:19,590 --> 00:41:20,440
Sir...

883
00:41:22,880 --> 00:41:23,670
Sir...

884
00:41:28,360 --> 00:41:29,510
Are you okay?

885
00:41:35,800 --> 00:41:38,030
You're sweating a lot, sir.

886
00:41:39,710 --> 00:41:40,630
Sir,

887
00:41:41,110 --> 00:41:42,510
I have a tea house

888
00:41:43,030 --> 00:41:44,070
right in front.

889
00:41:44,550 --> 00:41:47,150
Why don't you come with me and have some tea

890
00:41:47,440 --> 00:41:48,520
to beat the heat?

891
00:42:29,780 --> 00:42:31,070
Stop stealing food!

892
00:42:32,750 --> 00:42:34,920
A spiritual soul is attached to this vine, right?

893
00:42:34,920 --> 00:42:35,590
A spiritual soul that was detached

894
00:42:35,590 --> 00:42:37,000
from the body over 20 years ago.

895
00:42:37,000 --> 00:42:37,730
How strange.

896
00:42:37,760 --> 00:42:39,320
Why hasn't it disappeared yet?

897
00:42:39,320 --> 00:42:40,840
What did you use to keep it alive?

898
00:42:40,840 --> 00:42:41,700
What are you...

899
00:42:42,030 --> 00:42:43,230
No, that's not right.

900
00:42:43,230 --> 00:42:44,840
Even if it is nourished with the Blood Chalcedony,

901
00:42:44,840 --> 00:42:46,970
it shouldn't have such strong energy.

902
00:42:47,360 --> 00:42:48,320
Could it be...

903
00:42:49,150 --> 00:42:49,760
Ranran!

904
00:42:50,280 --> 00:42:51,590
Just a misunderstanding!

905
00:42:51,590 --> 00:42:52,190
Calm down.

906
00:42:52,320 --> 00:42:52,920
Calm down.

907
00:42:54,030 --> 00:42:54,830
Liang Wumeng,

908
00:42:54,920 --> 00:42:55,670
you're injured and having a secluded session.

909
00:42:55,670 --> 00:42:56,460
Shouldn't you be resting and recovering

910
00:42:56,460 --> 00:42:58,120
instead of making a mess here?

911
00:42:58,190 --> 00:42:59,280
You wanna die or what?

912
00:42:59,280 --> 00:43:00,080
Liang Wumeng?

913
00:43:00,840 --> 00:43:01,880
Master Liang!

914
00:43:09,710 --> 00:43:10,570
Please help me.

915
00:43:11,030 --> 00:43:12,030
Alright, young lady.

916
00:43:12,030 --> 00:43:12,960
No need to beg me.

917
00:43:15,230 --> 00:43:15,960
Young lady,

918
00:43:16,400 --> 00:43:18,070
I'm starting to take a liking to you.

